data.description:
NESTLED IN A PICTURESQUE LOCATION WITH BREATHTAKING MOUNTAIN VIEWS FROM THE BACK OF THE PROPERTY, THIS HOME IS A TRUE GEM! WELCOME HOME!
This well maintained home offers many upgrades making it very desirable. Upon entering you'll be greeted by a foyer that opens up to a large spacious great room, boasting a generous floor plan that provides ample space for both relaxation and entertaining. The centerpiece of the great room is a remarkable 16 ft wide patio door,  seamlessly merges the indoor and outdoor living spaces. Whether your hosting a gathering or simply enjoying a quiet evening, this feature creates an inviting and versatile atmosphere.
Moving onto the Gourmet kitchen, you will find many upgrades such as the stainless double ovens, with a large gas cooktop, Granite countertops and a large walk-in pantry! This home has plenty of storage for all your needs.
The split 4 car extended garage will be sure to impress! Room for all your toys!! Has an RV gate and room to build an RV garage!
This is a must see home!
